query:
SELECT u.id, u.email, u.name, u.role, u.openId, tp.id as profile_id, tp.approvalStatus
FROM users u
INNER JOIN tutor_profiles tp ON u.id = tp.userId
WHERE u.openId IS NULL
ORDER BY u.id;
